			<section class="comment-content comment">
				<p>Eli, </p>
<p>It would seem then, that the rate of decay of a non-optimal cultural area is far less than that of a non-optimal currency area. It only took the EU approximately 12 to 13 years to basically become completely unworkable, whereas the US has experienced but one civil war in the 223 year period since the constitution went into effect.</p>
<p>Why do you think that is?</p>
							</section><!-- .comment-content -->

			<div class="reply">
